```

### Option 2: Run offline demo mode

If internet access is not working, run:

```bash
python main.py --demo
```

This uses synthetic stock-like data so the project can still be demonstrated.

### Option 3: Try logistic regression instead of random forest

```bash
python main.py --ticker MSFT --start 2018-01-01 --end 2024-01-01 --model logistic_regression
```

